                            <comment id="405005" author="pjones" created="Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:33:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.16&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="404930" author="gerrit" created="Fri, 23 Feb 2024 07:10:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;Oleg Drokin &amp;lt;green@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&quot; merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/52147/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/52147/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
